- A page that gives a desctiption of 1 paragraph of a few programming languages of your choice

- The's a heading and a pragraph for each programming language
- Initally, only around 100 characters are shown for each paragraph.
- There is a 'Show More' button for each programming language
- When user clicks 'Show More' button:
  - The whole paragraph is shown
  - The button text changes to 'Show Less'
- When the 'Show Less' button is clicked:
  - The button text changes to 'Show More'
  - The paragraph again hides most of its text